om mock catalogs\nwith built-in galaxy assembly bias. We show that a simple matching of galaxy\nproperties to (sub)halo properties, such as mass and age, can recover the\nobserved environmental trends in ECO galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2020 21:08:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-18"}
