 occurring for stars at the turnoff. At\nsuper-solar bulk metallicity, various indicators agree on a cluster age between\nabout 3.5 and 4.0 Gyr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2020 01:57:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
