arameters. For a homogeneous system\nof users that all have the same decoding capabilities, we show that this\nequates to a simple maximum number of users per cluster constraint and propose\na lower complexity NOMA-best beam (NOMA-BB) algorithm. Simulation results\ndemonstrate the performance superiority in terms of sum rate compared to\northogonal multiple access (OMA) and traditional NOMA\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2020 14:48:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
